"illustrate using *urllib*, with enough detail about HTTP to help you "
"through. It is not intended to replace the :mod:`urllib.request` docs, but "
"is supplementary to them."
msgstr ""
"对于简单场景而言， *urlopen* 用起来十分容易。但只要在打开 HTTP URL "
